## Power Clean EMOM [HIIT]

- emom 10min:
  - Power Clean 3rep @70kg

## Alternating EMOM [HIIT]

- emom 12min alternating:
  - Deadlift 5rep @100kg
  - Strict Press 7rep @40kg
  - Toes-To-Bar 10rep

## Mixed EMOM [HIIT]

- every 2min for 20min:
  - Wall Ball 15rep @9kg
  - Box Jump 10rep

## Murph [HIIT]

- for-time:
  - run 1mile
  - Pull-Up 100rep
  - Push-Up 200rep
  - Air Squat 300rep
  - run 1mile

## Metcon [HIIT]

- amrap 12min:
  - Pull-Up 5rep
  - Push-Up 10rep
  - Air Squat 15rep
